          <title>Clayton leads Florida to NCAA title game, scoring 34 points in 79-73 victory over SEC rival Auburn</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Walter Clayton Jr. scored 34 points and Florida beat Southeastern Conference rival Auburn 79-73 in the Final Four on Saturday night, sending the Gators to the national championship game for the first time since their titles in 2006 and 2007.]]></description>
